{"id":646336,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":15}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"体育场","column":"","genre":"","count":"193","ytitle":"","mtitle":"希望之星","ftitle":"——献给上海的体育健儿们","authors":["宫玺"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"官玺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一颗古莲子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉睡千秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，终于发芽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华民族的雄心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖落历史的尘埃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，终于重放光华!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地平线上又巨人般地站起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江水似的灵活，泰山石似的挺拔!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从雄健的体魄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世人可看我民族的精魂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从轩昂的气度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环球感受我襟怀的阔大!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是“扬子江上初升的太阳”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中国升起的希望之星!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，愿灿烂的星辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自祖国四方纷纷升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉映每一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光耀海角天涯!"}]}